WEBVTT

00:06.068 --> 00:07.599
Will papa get better?

00:08.351 --> 00:10.132
Yeah. He will, yeah.

00:10.476 --> 00:11.563
He won't wake.

00:11.713 --> 00:12.799
I kept trying.

00:12.972 --> 00:14.237
How do you sleep at night?

00:14.388 --> 00:16.437
I support an entire village in Chiapas.

00:16.587 --> 00:18.634
- What do you do?
- What do I do for Mexico?

00:18.784 --> 00:20.317
Hey! Take it easy!

00:20.467 --> 00:23.112
There's millions of migrants working
on farms in this state.

00:23.262 --> 00:25.262
You can't turn it around
all by yourself.

00:29.309 --> 00:31.328
Tell them to send everything they have
and then...

00:31.656 --> 00:33.902
Oh God, are you okay? No, Bob.

00:34.052 --> 00:35.040
Just leave it.

00:36.582 --> 00:37.583
What's wrong Bob?

00:40.198 --> 00:41.941
Everything is fine Weston.

00:42.612 --> 00:44.746
If there's something wrong with my eyes,

00:45.583 --> 00:46.844
I can't do my job.

00:46.994 --> 00:49.157
And this lab, it's all that I have.

00:49.917 --> 00:51.610
I'm really scared, David.

